pub=Hindman+Settlement+School&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindmansettlement.org%2Fabout_us%2Fmission.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKatherine+Pettit\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-berea-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-berea_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-berea_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.berea.edu/hutchinslibrary/specialcollections/saa10.asp\">\"Southern Appalachian Archives: Guide to Pine Mountain Settlement School Collection\"</a>. Berea College<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-03-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Southern+Appalachian+Archives%3A+Guide+to+Pine+Mountain+Settlement+School+Collection&amp;rft.pub=Berea+College&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.berea.edu%2Fhutchinslibrary%2Fspecialcollections%2Fsaa10.asp&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKatherine+Pettit\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-pmss_about-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-pmss_about_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pinemountainsettlementschool.com/about.php\">\"About PMSS\"</a>. Pine Mountain Settlement School<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-03-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=About+PMSS&amp;rft.pub=Pine+Mountain+Settlement+School&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pinemountainsettlementschool.com%2Fabout.php&a